9. 
Ultrasonic Bath 
10. Hot Plate with Magnetic Stirrer 
11. Precession Michelson Interferometer 
3.23.2 Research Fields: 
Students of MS in Physics are doing research in the 
following field: 
1. Optics 
2. Material Science 
2. Space Physics 
3. Electronics 
4. Quantum Computing 
5. Medical Physics 
6. Theoretical / Experimental Physics & Relevant 
Fields. 
