4.3.3  
M.S. in Data Engineering and Information Management 
1- 
M.S. students may be required to study Non-Credit (NC) courses, in case they have not studied them at undergraduate 
level. All Non-Credit Courses are essentially required to be taken as soon as they offered. 
2- 
All the admitted students to M.S. Programme in Data Engineering will be required to take 10 courses in total including five 
compulsory along with other five courses from electives. 
