5 
NUMBER OF SEATS, FEES AND DEPOSIT 
5(a) 
NUMBER OF SEATS TO BE OFFERED FOR ADMISSION TO THE PROGRAMME 
Number of seats available to candidates in respective department who fulfill the requirements for 
eligibility as specified in the regulations shall be notified by each Department separately. 
5(b) 
UNIVERSITY FEES AND DEPOSIT 
The following are the University fees: 
1- 
Fee Payable at the time of admission to the Programme 
(i) 
Admission / Re-admission Fee  
Rs. 5000.00 
(ii) 
Enrolment fee (alongwith form fee) 
Rs. 2500.00 
(iii) 
Security Deposit  
Rs. 10000.00 
(iv) 
Documents Verification Fee 
Rs. 3000.00 
2- 
Fee Payable in each semester 
(i) 
Tuition & Examination Fee per Course 
EVENING  
a) 
M.Engg. Programme  
Rs. 17000.00 
b) 
MS Programme  
Rs. 17000.00 
c) 
MEM Programme  
Rs. 17000.00 
WEEKEND  
a) 
M.Engg. Programme  
Rs. 26000.00 
b) 
MS Programme  
Rs. 26000.00 
c) 
MEM Programme  
Rs. 26000.00 
(ii) 
Library Fee 
Rs. 1000.00 
(iii) 
Registration Fee / Semester 
Rs. 1500.00 
(iv) 
Internet Fee  
Rs. 1500.00 
(v) 
Late Fee, if applicable 
Rs. 1500.00 
(vi) 
Equivalence Fee, if applicable 
Rs. 1500.00 
(vii) 
University Endowment Fund 
Rs. 400.00 
(viii) I Grade Examinations Fee  
Rs. 10000.00 
(Per Course), if applicable
