6.2.5 Cancellation of Admission 
The admission of any such student will be 
cancelled if the student is: 
i) 
involved in any breach of discipline as 
prescribed in Regulations. 
ii) fails to register in any semester without being 
officially allowed withdrawal either from the 
Semester or from the Programme. 
iii) On probation in the second effective 
semester 
of 
his/her 
studies 
and 
on 
