7.4.1 Centre of Continuing Engineering Education 
(CCEE) 
Centre for Continuing Engineering Education, 
the most active wing of NED Academy enables 
professionals to attain higher levels of research, 
teaching and industrial cooperation for technical 
leaders for constant learning by empowering 
them with the relevant knowledge, skills, 
