 
Reverse Engineering 
– 
STRATASYS Fused Deposition Modeling 
Machine  
– 
FARO ARM Portable CMM  
– 
LASER SCANNER for scanning 3D parts 
 
Automation & Controls: 
– 
Programmable Logic Controllers,  
– 
Robotic arms,  
– 
Various types of transducers and sensors. 
 
Automatic Injection Molding Machine 
 
