 The textile machinery present in the 
department could be used for manufacturing 
different types of fabrics and yarns. Most of 
these machines are of industrial scale so they 
can be easily used for conducting research 
work. 
9.2 RESEARCH AREAS 
Looking at the expertise of our faculty 
members and the facilities available in the 
department, we can cover the following 
research areas: 
