faculty 
member, 
reviewed by BOS and approved by 
ASRB. 
(b) The scholar is required to 
successfully pass these courses within 
a twelve- month period. This period 
can be extended by a further six 
months with approval of concerned 
Dean on the recommendations of 
Supervisor and Chairperson. 
